{"tid":1881122,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"小英才是「好打得」 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-02-15T10:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T11:32:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb111bb4c2aeb087f770312cbe885788a25e3ea","tid":1881122,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200215/20862641/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200215%2F20862641%2F&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=d6fa9b38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200215%2F20862641%2F&h=a8b05e53\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200215/20862641/</a><br />\n<br />\n小英才是「好打得」 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200215/large/1581729311_b417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200215%2Flarge%2F1581729311_b417.jpg&h=a5cdcd85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n150名台籍旅客被困宿霧、馬尼拉等機場，被菲律賓拒絕入境的事，在台灣引起軒然大波。菲律賓為討好中國，匆匆推出禁令，以「一個中國」為由，把中、港、澳、台「平等」看待，不但擾亂了台灣旅客的行程，更大大激怒台灣當局。台灣政府已邀集外交、經濟、衛福與農業等單位研究對策，<span style=\"color: orange;\">若菲律賓不肯取消對台灣的旅遊禁令，台灣當局很可能使用七至八種手段制裁菲律賓，包括取消現行對菲國試行的免簽、凍結菲勞輸入等。</span><br />\n<br />\n凍結菲勞輸入，很可能令中產反感。但國家尊嚴無價，為維護國家及其國民的尊嚴，相信台灣政府會爭取到底。甚麼是「好打得」？這就是了。至於那種向極權諂媚，為一己之私利極盡擦鞋之能事，利用手上的權力向手無寸鐵的平民發動一次又一次攻擊的人，不是「好打得」，而是懦弱與無恥。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文溫柔端莊，但花名叫「小辣椒」，執善固執，為實現自己的政治理念，不介意迎難而上，在任期間推行年金改革，不惜得罪軍公教人員，不介意流失選民，不介意個人得失，做她競選時答應要做的事，要為年輕人留下一個更好的台灣，這就是一個從政者的膽識和魄力，是真正的「好打得」。<span style=\"color: orange;\">看看香港那個不知所謂的廢物，連「主流民意令我無法擔任特首，我會辭職」的個人承諾都不敢兌現，死皮賴臉戀棧權位，卻能力欠奉，尸位素餐，實在是不要臉。 </span><br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n==================<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/PCYXLFUOJZU3TKLOLH3U6GDUCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FPCYXLFUOJZU3TKLOLH3U6GDUCI%2F&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=2a90b031\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FPCYXLFUOJZU3TKLOLH3U6GDUCI%2F&h=d4764e35\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/PCYXLFUOJZU3TKLOLH3U6GDUCI/</a><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓即日解除對台旅遊禁令<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200215/large/1581698431_0308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200215%2Flarge%2F1581698431_0308.jpg&h=b9fd5294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇貞昌指台灣口罩日產千萬片，是第二大生產地。 台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓衞生部10日稱，在世衞「一中原則」下將台灣併入「中國旅遊禁令」之列，引台灣不滿，甚至也引內閣激辯。<span style=\"color: orange;\">菲國總統府發言人昨聲明，稱菲國跨部門工作小組決定解除對台灣旅行禁令，立即生效。</span>台灣外交部對此表示肯定，同時籲世衞回歸專業與中立，盡速更正對台的不當列示。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：香港家居隔離者擅往公院求診<br />\n<br />\n台政府口罩廠投產<br />\n<br />\n事緣菲律賓總統杜特爾特本月2日發指示，禁菲律賓人前往大陸及其特別行政區，以及14日內曾赴上述區域的外籍人士不得入境；詎料菲國衞生部10日突然宣佈，上述指示涵蓋台灣，因世衞把台歸在「中國」疫區下，引起台灣不滿。中央社指，菲國內閣特別小組昨午在總統府開會，討論解除「台灣禁令」。<span style=\"color: orange;\">菲匿名官員轉述，菲駐台機構與勞工部都力促解禁，以免15萬在台菲國工人受累。</span><br />\n<br />\n壓力下菲昨終宣佈解除對台旅行禁令，台外交部同時嚴正向世衞呼籲「公衞防疫無涉政治，WHO應回歸專業與中立，盡速更正對台不當列示」。此外台灣行政院長蘇貞昌昨視察口罩製造廠，確定政府購置的60部機順利投產，今日首批機器會上線。他表示在政府與民間協力下，交付機器時間由半年縮減至1個月，預計台灣2月底、3月初可日產1,000萬口罩，成為全球第二大口罩生產重鎮。"},{"pid":"8dce1d0154a374a56c5630501d2c33d3353a0bcb","tid":1881122,"uid":75823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭只係地方官，點可以同中華民國總統相提並論"},{"pid":"53a88b9beadea291ac559263599ed6256dfbee93","tid":1881122,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da83354c614069a981beca39761813673ae3eeac","tid":1881122,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cc5f41dc8bdf4c01fd71076a31775b65bb8f8b","tid":1881122,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天時地利人才<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=509be594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"33291350a981c848f13d1cf3e1bbc352b60c8e49","tid":1881122,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9811e9a9740af908dc3cbec8210ab9eb1c927bc3","tid":1881122,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"禁菲傭，香港件廢物唔敢玩咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217f3543a7d8fc782c86b057d1899c523573bd1c","tid":1881122,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b699eb46e1784e646a350f0